main event: A UFO sighting occurred in Yorba Linda, California on August 28, 1966.
interesting points: The case was marked as 'INSUFFICIENT DATA FOR EVALUATION',The document is part of Project Blue Book, which investigated UFO sightings in the U.S.,The report mentions that it was initially submitted as a civilian sighting,The length of observation and the course of the object were not reported,There are no photographs or physical evidence associated with this sighting.
witness description: A civilian who reported the sighting.
